race.comment: ANJO PRINCE (6) is yet to miss the placings in an excellent record this track and trip which boasts three wins and three placings. Comes off a (18.17) win last time, scoring by 4 lengths in a Grade 5 over 320m at this track. Looks a leading chance on best. FIRST ON BASE (1) hit the ground running last start and was never headed to land his maiden success over 320m at this track (18.30). Boxed well here. Must include in calculations. FEDERAL NOTICE (3) is an honest type in the frame at nine of 15 starts including last time when second (22.42) over 388m at Gosford. Super consistent and can feature with the right run. BAKERLOO BOY (7) can feature with the right run.
